race.description: Nixon's Function Centre (Queens) Stake Pr2 Divisio
race.comment: TUNGKILLO (1) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Hi There Frank (23.02) in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings three times from six starts. Top prospect. PRINCESS TILLEY (7) scored two back then was always well back and could manage only a 6 length 8th at Angle Park (31.22). Must be included in calculations. WIRRULLA MELVY (3) was out of the placings last time but shapes well for this on her strong win the start prior, getting around Angle Park over 342m in 19.61. Should be in this for a long way. OUR IVIE ROSE (8) is worth including after a top-three finish at big odds most recently.
